---
title: Hearty Chicken Drumsticks & Red Wine Jus with Steamed Broccoli
description: The best things in life take time, and this dish is no exception. Sit back and let the clock transform chicken drumsticks into melt-in-your-mouth goodness in a rich, red-wine based sauce. Served over silky mashed potatoes with tender broccoli, this meal is well worth the wait.
